Q0xJUFMuQzMuNzIwLmRhc2hfYmFzZWxpbmVfMV92MSIsInhwdl9hc3NldF9pZCI6MjU5MzMxNjcyNDQ1MDAxMiwiYXNzZXRfYWdlX2RheXMiOjEwLCJ2aV91c2VjYXNlX2lkIjoxMDA5OSwiZHVyYXRpb25fcyI6NDQsInVybGdlbl9zb3VyY2UiOiJ3d3cifQ%3D%3D&ccb=17-1&vs=1ce256279d33132b&_nc_&_nc_gid=WA1iS8NNtGIecAAK6m-Seg&_nc_ss=72a8c&_nc_zt=28&oh=00_AQCiw0rwm7-I9oSRA_WBoD68nXXpCVvvGn-Cc76SrdPA5w&oe=6A5DB9CB", "musicInfo": {"artist_name": "carolineasolomon", "song_name": "Original audio", "uses_original_audio": true, "should_mute_audio": false, "should_mute_audio_reason": "", "audio_id": "27869907916033307"}, "ownerUsername": "carolineasolomon", "ownerFullName": "Caroline Solomon", "transcript": "Here's how to tell if your cat is happy, featuring my cat Sweetie. They curl up like a shrimp, which means they're comfortable and ready for deep rest. Sorry Sweetie, didn't mean to wake you. They want to hang out with you and follow you from room to room. Time for bed Sweetie! They make biscuits. When your cat kneads blankets, pillows, or even you, it's a behavior they learned as kittens, and it's a sign they feel safe and relaxed. They have loose whiskers. When their whiskers fan out softly to the sides of their face, this means your cat is relaxed and content. Their litter box habits stay consistent. And that's all thanks to Sweetie's favorite litter, Pretty Litter. Sweetie can't get enough of Pretty Litter because it's lightweight, unscented, and the pebble-like silica crystals are comfortable on her sensitive paws. Check out Pretty Litter, which is now available on TikTok Shop."}, {"shortCode": "DaduFWPy2xg", "url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/DaduFWPy2xg/", "caption": "Adhd-friendly home organization tips! @slice_cuts #home #homeorganization #declutter #adhd #adhdtips", "timestamp": "2026-07-06T20:14:09.000Z", "videoDuration": 49.201, "videoPlayCount": 11121, "videoViewCount": 5179, "likesCount": 309, "commentsCount": 1, "displayUrl": "https://scontent-atl3-3.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/736367789_18119567452828197_44843